claim.claim-text:
A foreign object detector comprising:
a detection coil;
a transmitting circuit generating RF power of a predetermined frequency;
a directional coupler outputting the RF power supplied from the transmitting circuit to the detection coil, and extracting reflected power that is a power component reflected by the detection coil; and
a detection circuit receiving the reflected power extracted by the directional coupler, and detecting a foreign object by sensing a change in frequency characteristic of the reflected power.
